snippet.title: Kick Bot - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Barely touch the ground as you chain together wall-jumps, slides, dashes, and butt stomps through seven unique worlds filled with tough-as-nails traps and puzzles! You'll be surprised what you can do with only TWO-BUTTONS, quick reflexes, and a sharp mind!


Source: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=T9_QAEbioMM
Kick Bot on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1136290/Kick_Bot


#KickBot #trailer #gametrailers #games #gaming
